title: On The Avatars
author: zaphod100
pages:
#- The Avatars of The Bird

As all Brothers of The Flock know, The Bird has appeared to mortal man in four different forms. These Avatars have recently been examined and now we know the meaning of each of the four forms.
#- The Avatar known as Monograms represents the strength and courage of The Bird. This is the form he took for combat when defending the people. He used this form when he first made Nest in Augusta, signifying that he wanted to make it safe. 
#- He had a full combat loadout on this form at all times lest his Flock be threatened.
#- The Avatar known as endors_toi represents The Birds anger and madness. This is evident by the crazy colored skin that this form appeared with. He used this avatar for good when he frequently AFKed farms
#- with it but also for mad purposes such as The Prank on Tallen and The Scourge of Augusta.
#- The Avatar known as JakSpringTooth represents the mystery of The Bird. This was The Birds true form aeons ago. Beyond that we know little. This form was shown only very rarely. The Bird only took this form for the most mysterious of uses.
#- The final Avatar of The Bird New_Yardbird is also His true form. This form represents the unity of The Bird. He is all the forms at once. This is the form He normally took to do business and to live among us. This is The Form that built and destroyed.
#-  This is the form we revere. 
#- Hail The Bird. May we soar with him forever and may he one day fly back to us.

Caw. 
#- 